snippet.title: Revenge of the Savage Planet Announcement | Official GamesCom ONL Trailer
snippet.description:
From the Creators of Journey to the Savage Planet.  The Official New Announcement Trailer of Revenge of the Savage Planet Revealed During Gamescom Opening Night Live.

“WELCOME BACK EXPLORER! Entry-level recruits of the Universe’s Largest and Most Successful Company, Alta InterGlobal - your new employer - have been reassigned to a new corporate initiative to help humanity find a safe home in deep space. Should be fine.
Have fun!”
